title: Appointments in General Practice
description: The aim of the publication is to inform users about activity and usage of GP appointments historically and how primary care is impacted by seasonal pressures, such as winter.
datasetNotes: On the landing page scroll to latest version, this will pen another page scroll down to resources select the XLS spreadsheet.
sizingNotes: A number of simple tables with footnotes each table is a different format
notes: The publication is one of a series, with each publication giving detailed information for a single month, and summary time series information
